Pepperdine and UCLA among others, and Beck give the Chargers a solid middle, 
and Thompson, Coblenz, and Soriano add to El Toro's depth. "I've never had this 
many guys who can really play," Jagd said. "I look forward to our practices . . 
. it should be a fun year." 
