<HEADLINE>
<P>
1994 BOYS' VOLLEYBALL PREVIEW; SIX TEAMS TO WATCH; DANA HILLS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Coach: Oz Simmons (12th year). 
</P>
<P>
 1993: 7-10, 5-5 in the South Coast League. Finished fourth in league and did 
not qualify for Division I playoffs. 
</P>
<P>
 Key returners: Matt Clem, 6-4, middle blocker, Sr.; Jeremy Darner, 6-5, 
outside hitter, Sr.; Bob Hefty, 6-8, middle blocker, Sr.; Neil Hewko, 6-4, 
outside hitter, Sr.; Wesley Tsai, 5-9, setter, Sr. 
</P>
<P>
